<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='153:179'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0157', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='179:195'>欽定四庫全書　　　　　經部一</span>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='195:211'>　易例　　　　　　　　　易類</span>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='211:217'>　　提要</span>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='217:234'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案易例二卷</span>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='234:257'>　　　國朝惠棟撰棟所作周易述後目録列有易微</span>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='257:280'>　　　　言等七書惟易微言二卷已附刋卷末其餘</span>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='280:303'>　　　　並闕此易例二卷即七書中之第三種近始</span>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='303:326'>　　　　刋板于潮陽皆考究漢儒之傳以發明易之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='326:352'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0157', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='352:375'>　　　　本例凡九十類其中有録無書者十三類原</span>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='375:398'>　　　　跋稱為未成之本今考其書非惟採摭未完</span>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='398:421'>　　　　即門目亦尚未分意棟欲鎔鑄舊説作為易</span>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='421:444'>　　　　例先剏草本採摭漢儒易説隨手題識筆之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='444:467'>　　　　于冊以儲作論之材其標目有當為例而立</span>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='467:490'>　　　　一類者亦有不當為例而立一類者有一類</span>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='490:513'>　　　　為一例者亦有一類為數例者如既有扶陽</span>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='513:536'>　　　　抑陰一類又有陽道不絶陰道絶義一類又</span>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='536:562'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0157', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='562:585'>　　　　有陽無死義一類此必欲作扶陽抑隂一例</span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='585:608'>　　　　而襍録于三處者也曰中和曰詩尚中和曰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='608:631'>　　　　禮樂尚中和曰君道尚中和曰建國尚中和</span>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='631:654'>　　　　曰春秋尚中和分為六類已極繁複而其後</span>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='654:677'>　　　　又出中和一類君道中和一類卷末更出中</span>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='677:700'>　　　　和之本一類此亦必欲作易尚中和一例而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='700:723'>　　　　散見于九處者也古者有聖人之徳然後居</span>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='723:746'>　　　　天子之位一類徴引繁蕪與易例無闗而題</span>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='746:772'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0157', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='772:795'>　　　　下注曰即二升坤五義此必摭為乾升坤降</span>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='795:818'>　　　　之佐証而偶置在前者也如初為元士一類</span>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='818:841'>　　　　即貴賤類中之一乾為仁震為車艮為言三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='841:864'>　　　　類即諸例中之三天地之始一類即卦無兑</span>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='864:887'>　　　　天一類之複出皆由未及排貫遂似散錢滿</span>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='887:911'>　　　　屋至于史記讀易之文漢書𫝊易之派更與</span>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='911:935'>　　　　易例無與亦必存為佐證之文而𫝊寫者誤</span>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='935:958'>　　　　為本書也如此者不一而足均不可據為定</span>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='958:984'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0157', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='984:1007'>　　　　本然棟于諸經深窺古義其所捃摭大抵老</span>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1007:1030'>　　　　師宿儒専門授受之微㫖一字一句具有淵</span>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1030:1053'>　　　　源苛汰其蕪襍存其菁英因所録而排比叅</span>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1053:1077'>　　　　稽之猶可以見聖人作易之大綱漢代𫝊經</span>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1077:1100'>　　　　之崖畧正未可以殘缺少緒竟棄其稿矣乾</span>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1100:1116'>　　　　隆四十三年七月恭校上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1116:1148'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1148:1173'>　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span>
